Text: Thank you for this interesting comic series. Waiting to read future issues)
Nice! I've been missing 2/3 of these forever. Thanks.

The initial 6 issue mini series just finished in August.  Tom Hutchison (writer), Alisson Borges (artist), and Kate Finnegan (colorist) are working on the first 5 issue story arc of the new series which should debuted at the New York Comic Con just over a week ago.  Three issue #1 variant covers are available for sale in Big Dog Ink's store, but not the normal issue #1 yet.
